OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fbrightness this evening and a few
OL,7,Fshowers. Becoming dry with clear
OL,8,Fperiods overnight across all parts. A
OL,9,Fcold night with a slight frost in
OL,10,Fsheltered glens.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA dry morning with some early
OL,13,Fbrightness. Then outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fwill spread northeast in the afternoon
OL,15,Fand evening. Becoming windy with
OL,16,Fsoutheasterly gales along exposed
OL,17,Fcoasts in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
