OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSunny
OL,6,Fintervals and the chance of a few
OL,7,Fshowers on Saturday, but some dry
OL,8,Fweather too. More in the way of
OL,9,Fshowers on Sunday and Monday.
